Modular Arithmetic   |
----------------------
Why modulo needed ?
to limit range

2^10 = 1024 â‰ˆ 10^3.

Properties:
1. Addition =>
    ( a + b ) % m = ( a % m + b % m ) % m
    ( a + m ) % m = a % m

2. Multiplication
    ( a * b ) % m = (( a % m ) * (b % m )) % m

3. Subtraction ( special )
    ( a - b ) % m = ( ( a % m ) - ( b % m ) + m ) % m

4. Reminder
    a % m = ((( a % m ) % m ) % m ) % m

5. Exponentiation
    a^b % m = (( a % m )^b ) % m



